---
title: Fragrant Satay Chicken & Veggie Curry with Rapid Rice
description: A satay chicken curry, it has our hearts fluttering and our mouths watering as the hearty curry aromas sweep the kitchen. On a bed of fluffy rice, we’re head over heels for this curry!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

